nesting
Allows you to nest selectors.
a {
  /* direct nesting (& MUST be the first part of selector)*/
  & span {
    color: white;
  }

  /* @nest rule (for complex nesting) */
  @nest span & {
    color: blue;
  }

  /* media query automatic nesting */
  @media (min-width: 30em) {
    color: yellow;
  }
}

